data.description: Welcome to 549 Cherrywood Lane in the desirable Encore at Heisley Park community.  This beautiful 4 bedroom home is modern and sleek with enough opportunity to let you make it yours.  Master bedroom has 2 walk in closets and en suite bath.  Two of the other 3 bedrooms have very large walk in closets in addition to nicely sized rooms.  Additionally there is a fabulous bonus room upstairs that could double as an office, family room or playroom.  Kitchen features gorgeous granite countertops, beautiful colored cabinets and island and stainless steel dishwasher, stove and microwave.  The basement is just waiting for you to put your creative skills to use and already has rough ins for bathroom plumbing.  Grab your favorite realtor and come see this beautiful home and make it yours!
